high_descs: Turn Right and walk to the blue coffee machine.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge, then pick up the mug from the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the mug in the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in the sink on the right.

high_descs: turn around and locate the coffee maker
pick up the mug from the coffee maker
turn right towards the fridge
place the mug in the fridge to cool for some time and take it out
turn around and locate the sink
place the mug in the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cold mug in the sink

high_descs: Move to the coffee pot to the right of the sink.
Pick up the mug from the pot.
Move to the fridge to the right of you.
Place the cup inside the fridge and chill for a moment before removing it and closing the door.
Move to the sink to the left of the coffee pot.
Place the cup inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the stove then turn right and head to the coffee maker
pick up the mug that is sitting in the coffee maker
turn right and head to the black fridge across the room
Open the fridge and place the cup in the freezer to the left of the bread. Close the fridge. Then open the fridge and pick up the mug
Turn around and cross the room to the sink
Place the mug in the right section of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a cold mug in a sink

high_descs: Turn around to the right and walk up to the blue coffee maker on the kitchen counter
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and walk over to the fridge
Put the mug into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink
Put the mug in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Watch the head of lettuce fall off of the counter and turn around to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the freezer, place the mug inside the freezer next to the loaf of bread, close the freezer, wait a few seconds, take the mug out of the freezer, and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the mug inside of the sink.
